### 개선 #2: QueryDSL Projection으로 필요한 컬럼만 조회

**After (QueryDSL Projection):**
```kotlin
// domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/follow/CustomFollowRepositoryImpl.kt
class CustomFollowRepositoryImpl(
    private val queryFactory: JPAQueryFactory,
) : CustomFollowRepository {

    override fun findFollowingsWithUserInfo(
        followerId: String,
        limit: Int,
        offset: Int,
    ): List<FollowUserDto> {
        val follow = QFollowEntity.followEntity
        val user = QUserEntity.userEntity

        return queryFactory
            .select(
                Projections.constructor(
                    FollowUserDto::class.java,
                    follow.id,
                    user.id,
                    user.nickname,
                    user.profileImageUrl,
                    follow.createdAt,
                )
            )
            .from(follow)
            .innerJoin(user).on(follow.followingId.eq(user.id))
            .where(
                follow.followerId.eq(followerId),
                follow.deletedAt.isNull,
            )
            .orderBy(follow.createdAt.desc())
            .limit(limit.toLong())
            .offset(offset.toLong())
            .fetch()
    }
}
```

예상 개선: 전체 컬럼 조회 제거, 불필요한 UserEntity 연관 로딩 차단

